\sum_{s_b=0}^{k_1} \sum_{s_g=0}^{k_2} [k_1 - s_b = k_2 - s_g][s_b \le n+1][s_g \le n+1] \binom{n+k_1-s_b-1}{k_1-s_b} \binom{n+1}{s_b} \binom{n+1}{s_g}
= \sum_{s_b=0}^{\min(k_1, n+1)} [0 \le s_b + k_2 - k_1 \le \min(k_2, n+1)] \binom{n+k_1-s_b-1}{k_1-s_b} \binom{n+1}{s_b} \binom{n+1}{s_b + k_2 - k_1}
= \sum_{s_b=\max(0, k_1-k_2)}^{\min(k_1, n+1, n+1 + k_1 - k_2)} \binom{n+k_1-s_b-1}{k_1-s_b} \binom{n+1}{s_b} \binom{n+1}{s_b + k_2 - k_1}
